{"tid":730562,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插沙] 點樣合併多個excel工作簿?","createTime":"2018-07-05T13:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T03:58:53.000Z","uid":189523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4ddc0cefb98b75db55d78aa0ef072ee293add626","tid":730562,"uid":189523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"做project遇到個難題想請教巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有3個獨立既excel檔案 (當叫&quot;a&quot; ,&quot;b&quot;, &quot;c&quot;)<br />\n我想將a,b,c各檔案入面其中一頁既內容(相同格式,標題) <br />\n抽出黎然後係一個新既excel活頁簿(當叫&quot;all&quot;) 到合併show曬出黎<br />\n<br />\n我試過用excel 2016既query功能合併<br />\n初步係得既<br />\n但有以下幾個問題:<br />\n<br />\n1. 修改a,b,c檔內容後, 同步更新&quot;all&quot;會出現error, 有幾列全黑左<br />\n(會唔會係關原本a,b,c檔入面有好多formula事?)<br />\n<br />\n2. 有冇得合併埋a,b,c原檔既文字/設計格式? <br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇excel大師可以教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(有d複雜 1999 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"2c8b329ac1f0ce31d77e301412130f384e88d656","tid":730562,"uid":45174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:38:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://lmgtfy.com/?q=move+or+copy+worksheet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flmgtfy.com%2F%3Fq%3Dmove%2Bor%2Bcopy%2Bworksheet&d=XPF1Hx4JootJ9ygknFWLQDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=014cb7ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lmgtfy.com/?q=move+or+copy+worksheet</a>"},{"pid":"c76e185ece1614c84b66feb2b51171582d538352","tid":730562,"uid":179571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38051e3225438d3fe3c0499a87e7c7c9aff0272b","tid":730562,"uid":189523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c8b329ac1f0ce3