ue就會只抄值"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:14:52.000Z","msg":"每個檔案都需要用到formula<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我太蠢 睇完macro都唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下可以做到資料同步更新嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"有咩唔明？其實網上面啲料已經好齊，我自己都係無底靠網上學啲皮毛黎用，想要咩效果就唔識就google 打vba xxxxx，一般都有野抄，邊睇邊抄邊學<br />\n<br />\n基本上marco就係set指令控制excel自己做唔同動作，只要識寫loop就可以解決好多麻煩，我用開do同for，do就係一直loop到達到某個條件，基礎都係要加個n=n+1俾佢loop到停，for就係loop晒指定範圍既野就停"},{"pid":"e1c930a6fa44583e2c1bd5cd705d185c742ffa28","tid":730562,"uid":22557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:40:36.000Z","msg":"有同一個lookup value 咪直接用vlookup 咪得"},{"pid":"631efb6184a8ff062c8c27e3957c0d7fcb06bdda","tid":730562,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:55:23.000Z","msg":"用 VBA set 4 張 worksheet ，然後 define range (因為可能唔要 header) ，然後 .Copy method/.value 咁抄寫過去"},{"pid":"093f7466c0b63b0f9f17087dbe1f55edb4d724fd","tid":730562,"uid":162895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:58:53.000Z","msg":"A: <a href=\"http://ricky0512.blogspot.com/2016/10/excel-merge-files.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fricky0512.blogspot.com%2F2016%2F10%2Fexcel-merge-files.html&d=XPF1Hx4JootJ9ygknFWLQDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5d790d00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ricky0512.blogspot.com/2016/10/excel-merge-files.html</a><br />\n<br />\n先用A呢個VBA CODE將文件夾內所有EXCEL合併<br />\n<br />\nB: <a href=\"https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/1184-excel-merge-multiple-worksheets-into-one.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.extendoffice.com%2Fdocuments%2Fexcel%2F1184-excel-merge-multiple-worksheets-into-one.html&d=XPF1Hx4JootJ9ygknFWLQDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=4a6a7e19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/1184-excel-merge-multiple-worksheets-into-one.html</a><br />\n<br />\n再用B呢個VBA, 合併Excel內所有sheet (注意B呢款限死左要全部SHEET格式一樣先COPY到)"}]}